Dear Mr Ay Patient 1.

This is a reminder to update your record with how you are feeling today. It should only take a minute and will help your clinical team to manage your health.

Click on this link:
http://pkb-frontend-4/test/updateSymptoms.action

Why do I have to do this?
This helps your doctors, nurses and family to understand how your health is changing with time, illness and treatments. For example, if your doctor prescribed antibiotics for your chest infection, tracking the severity of your cough over time lets your team know how well you are recovering, or whether you need different antibiotics.

How do I do this?
Just click on the link above to log into your record. Then you can click on as many symptoms as you want to, for example "Cough", "Constipation" or "Tiredness".

Stop sending me these messages
Sorry for the inconvenience. To stop the messages click here:
http://pkb-frontend-4/auth/symptomReminderOptOut.action?personId=1646

Please do not reply to this email; this address is not monitored. Log into your record to see your medical information and manage your care.

Yours,

Patients Know Best Help Team

Dear Miss Ay Patient 2.

This is a reminder to update your record with how you are feeling today. It should only take a minute and will help your clinical team to manage your health.

Click on this link:
http://pkb-frontend-4/test/updateSymptoms.action

Why do I have to do this?
This helps your doctors, nurses and family to understand how your health is changing with time, illness and treatments. For example, if your doctor prescribed antibiotics for your chest infection, tracking the severity of your cough over time lets your team know how well you are recovering, or whether you need different antibiotics.

How do I do this?
Just click on the link above to log into your record. Then you can click on as many symptoms as you want to, for example "Cough", "Constipation" or "Tiredness".

Stop sending me these messages
Sorry for the inconvenience. To stop the messages click here:
http://pkb-frontend-4/auth/symptomReminderOptOut.action?personId=1653

Please do not reply to this email; this address is not monitored. Log into your record to see your medical information and manage your care.

Yours,

Patients Know Best Help Team
